OL,7,FNHS and Department of Health officials
OL,8,Fare complacent and "out of ideas" when
OL,9,Fit comes to transforming the health
OL,10,Fservice for patients, MPs have said.
OL,12,FThe Public Accounts Committee (PAC)
OL,13,Ffound that while the Government's
OL,14,Fambition for the NHS represents a
OL,15,F"golden opportunity", leaders at the
OL,16,FDepartment of Health and NHS England
OL,17,F(NHSE) are not ready to prioritise the
OL,18,Fshifts needed, instead arguing they
OL,19,Fare difficult and should take place
OL,20,Fslowly.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@aO]wD@AOUwD@TO]
