OL,3,CNHS and health department officials
OL,4,C'out of ideas' for transforming care `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FThe cross-party committee accused NHS
OL,8,FEngland of being "overly optimistic"
OL,9,Fregarding improving productivity in
OL,10,Fthe NHS, adding that the financial
OL,11,Fposition of the health service overall
OL,12,Fcontinues to worsen.
OL,14,FMPs said the Government's NHS
OL,15,Fambitions seem to "run counter to
OL,16,Fofficials' lack of ideas or drive to
OL,17,Fchange".
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@dO]wD@SOUyD@GO]
