OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FAn NHS England spokesman said the
OL,8,Freport contained "factual
OL,9,Finaccuracies" and productivity in the
OL,10,FNHS had doubled compared with before
OL,11,Fthe pandemic.
OL,13,FIn September, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer laid out plans for "three big
OL,15,Fshifts" in the NHS: moving from
OL,16,Fhospital-based to community care; from
OL,17,Fanalogue to digital; and from treating
OL,18,Fill health to preventing people
OL,19,Fgetting sick in the first place.
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@MO]vD@\OUwD@GO]
