OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FHowever, the PAC said that, under
OL,8,Fquestioning, officials from both the
OL,9,FDepartment for Health and Social Care
OL,10,F(DHSC) and NHS England do not seem
OL,11,Fready to take that on.
OL,13,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown,
OL,14,FConservative MP and chairman of the
OL,15,Fcommittee, said: "The current
OL,16,FGovernment has told the public that
OL,17,Fthe NHS is broken.
OL,19,F"This will not come as news to NHS
OL,20,Fpatients, nor to its hard-working
OL,21,Fstaff across the country.
OL,26,@wD@ROU{D@AOU
