OL,3,CNHS and health department officials
OL,4,C'out of ideas' for transforming care `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"Nor indeed does it to this committee,
OL,8,Fwhich has long warned of the systemic
OL,9,Fissues plaguing the NHS, issues which
OL,10,Fthe Government has transformative
OL,11,Fambitions to address.
OL,13,F"We were aghast then, to find amongst
OL,14,Fsenior officials in charge of
OL,15,Fdelivering these ambitions some of the
OL,16,Fworst complacency displayed to the PAC
OL,17,Fin my time serving on it.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
