OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"Given the position of the NHS,
OL,8,Fforcing this committee to wade through
OL,9,Ftreacle by mouthing the same stale
OL,10,Fplatitudes of incremental change is
OL,11,Fsimply not going to cut it."
OL,13,FThe report found that NHS England's
OL,14,F"long-held" ambition to move more care
OL,15,Ffrom hospitals to the community "has
OL,16,Fstalled".
