OL,7,FFurthermore, despite carrying out 15%
OL,8,Fmore planned activity compared with
OL,9,Fbefore the pandemic, the NHS is less
OL,10,Fproductive overall once the activities
OL,11,Fof mental health trusts, community
OL,12,Ftrusts and GPs are considered.
OL,14,FThe report said: "NHS England displays
OL,15,Fa remarkable complacency about the
OL,16,Frealisation of future NHS productivity
OL,17,Fimprovements, which, if achieved,
OL,18,Fwould be unprecedented.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
