OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"NHS England is confident that the
OL,8,Fannual productivity gains that it has
OL,9,Fcommitted to of 2% by 2028`29 can be
OL,10,Fachieved because it contends the last
OL,11,Ftwo years have been affected by
OL,12,Fongoing disruptions such as industrial
OL,13,Faction, and that further recovery is
OL,14,Fstill possible, particularly through
OL,15,Ftechnology-enabled change.
