OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"However, NHSE was unable to convince
OL,8,Fus that it has a detailed plan to
OL,9,Fachieve the promised productivity
OL,10,Fgains, and it does not yet fully
OL,11,Fmeasure and capture productivity in
OL,12,Fimportant areas, such as mental health
OL,13,Fand community services."
OL,15,FThe report also said that "the switch
OL,16,Fto digital in parts of the NHS has
OL,17,Fbeen glacially slow".
OL,19,FMoney intended for technology has had
OL,20,Fto be redirected to plug spending
OL,21,Fdeficits elsewhere.
