OL,7,FThe report noted that some NHS trusts
OL,8,Fstill rely on fax machines, while
OL,9,Fothers "are often still too reliant on
OL,10,Fpaper records".
OL,12,FThis is despite the fact that
OL,13,Fhospitals with electronic patient
OL,14,Frecords have productivity levels that
OL,15,Fare 13% higher than those without.
OL,17,FIn the study, the MPs argued the
OL,18,FDepartment of Health's and NHS
OL,19,FEngland's approach to NHS finances "is
OL,20,Ftypified by short-termism".
