OL,7,FThe report also condemned officials
OL,8,Ffor repeatedly failing to provide
OL,9,Finformation about budgets in good time
OL,10,Fto local NHS systems, saying there was
OL,11,F"disregard for basic principles of
OL,12,Fsound financial planning".
OL,14,FIt added: "Even as they write the new
OL,15,F10-year plan for the NHS, DHSC and
OL,16,FNHSE have not convinced us that they
OL,17,Fare ready to give the three big shifts
OL,18,Fdesired by government the priority
OL,19,Fthey need.
